    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-07-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-07-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="902"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d902">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Meyer</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-07-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 13, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Received official communication from Count Lamsdorff this morning that M. Witte
                    has been appointed in the place of Mouravieff on account of the latter’s health.
                    M. Witte, furnished with the full requisite powers, sails from Cherbourg
                    Wednesday, July 25. Due New York August 1.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Meyer.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
